Hi Chuck,
Would greatly depend on year of the bus and year of the cargo door latch  
that is operated by the outside door handle.
  Up to early 1964 this latch had no lock after this time the latch  had a 
built in interior lock.  The earlier latch can be modified to lock  from the 
interior.
 
